cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.NI 

This paper deals with optimization of distributed learning systems, which is a topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with communication and computation trade-offs, which is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes algorithms for decentralized training, which is a topic in distributed systems (cs.DS). The paper also deals with convergence analysis, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper deals with network bandwidth and latency, which is a topic in computer networks (cs.NI).
